catalog.title: Clothes
catalog.description: We need warm winter clothes. The sizes are for children from 2 to 14 years old. If possible, made from cotton materials, no superficial ones.

catalog.title: Toys
catalog.description: We need toys for babies under 1.5 years old, as well as some children books and puzzles for kids under 6 years old

catalog.title: School Supplies
catalog.description: We need 20 striped notebooks and 10 squared notebooks, 5 backpacks, and other school supplies, such as pens, pencils, rulers, erasers, etc.
